  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">high-capacity</span> <span class=\"name name-fuel\">antimatter-based fuel</span>, this cell harnesses an internal black hole generator to power <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship hyperdrives</span> across multiple warp jumps.<br><br>Cell walls are specially designed to reflect any reality paradoxes back towards the heart of the unit, where they generate additional power.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高容量</span><span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质燃料</span>。这种电池可利用内部黑洞生成器为<span class=\"name name-technology\">星际飞船超光速推进器</span>的多次曲速飞行供能。<br><br>特别设计的电池壁能将任何现实悖论反射回单元中心，并在那里产生额外的能量。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高容量</span><span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质燃料</span>。这种电池可利用内部黑洞生成器为<span class=\"name name-technology\">星际飞船超光速推进器</span>的多次曲速飞行供能。<br><br>特别设计的电池壁能将任何现实悖论反射回单元中心，并在那里产生额外的能量。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "本電池為<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高容量</span><span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物質燃料</span>，利用內部的黑洞能量源，提供<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船超空間驅動器</span>所需能量，可進行多次空間跳躍。<br><br>電池壁經特殊設計，可將任何現實悖論反射回單位中心，產生更多能量。"
  },
